    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">Read TASK-INDEX; confirm 059 complete.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">Read Fluent v9 patterns + Context-pane widget shape + event-types from 059.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Author Widget">`src/client/shared/Spaarke.AI.Widgets/src/widgets/context/ExecutionTraceWidget.tsx`. Subscribes to `context.*` events via PaneEventBus.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Build Timeline UI">Fluent v9 list + accordion components; per-event-type icon + colored band; auto-scroll on new entries; per-type collapsible filters.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Light/Dark Parity">Per ADR-021 dark-mode audit; verify token usage; capture screenshots.</step>
    <step order="6" name="ADR-015 Render Audit">Code review every render path — confirm no free-form content rendered; only typed enumerated fields. Document in task notes.</step>
    <step order="7" name="UI Tests">Per ui-test skill: render with mock events; verify timeline order; verify filters work; verify dark mode.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-012/015/021/030).</step>
